body.p:

		Verify build configuration file by running the build. In project root type in:
		uisdk-build	
		... you should get message:
		 (e): Default phases should be defined, (eg. "defaultPhase": "..." )	
		... add default phase to "build.json" and verify again.
		"build.json" should look like this:

{
    "properties": {
        "buildDir": "target"
    },
	"defaultPhase": "clean",
    "phases": {
        "clean": {
            "delete": {
                "target": "$(buildDir)"
            }
        }
    }
}
